Help!

01:55.316 --> 01:56.748
[banging on door]

01:56.817 --> 01:58.050
Help!

01:58.118 --> 01:59.818
Let me in!

01:59.820 --> 02:02.321
Hey, Lily, Lily, Lily,
Lily, Lily, please.

02:02.323 --> 02:03.522
